data.text:
A covered bridge shaded by sycamore trees crosses the San Lorenzo river in Felton, CA.

From Back: "OLD COVERED BRIDGE Felton, California Built in 1892, this old covered bridge spans the sycamore-shaded San Lorenzo River at Felton, California. Although replaced by a concrete bridge in 1938, it still remains as a picturesque link to the romantic past."
